<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 15:12:16 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>迪拜环球港务集团预计从亚洲到欧洲的货物成本将更高</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/dp-world-expects-cost-goods-asia-be-higher-europe-2024-01-16/</link><description>迪拜环球港务集团首席财务官尤夫拉吉·纳拉扬(Yuvraj Narayan)周二表示，他预计胡塞武装袭击船只造成的红海航运中断将对欧洲消费者造成最严重的打击。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 12:06:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/dp-world-expects-cost-goods-asia-be-higher-europe-2024-01-16/</guid></item><item><title>早间竞价：降息猫捉老鼠的游戏</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-01-16/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 11:02:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-01-16/</guid></item><item><title>碧桂园任命毕马威为离岸债务重组顾问</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/country-garden-appoints-kpmg-adviser-offshore-debt-restructuring-2024-01-16/</link><description>陷入困境的房地产开发商碧桂园周二表示，已任命毕马威咨询（中国）有限公司为其境外债务重组的首席财务顾问。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 10:59:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/country-garden-appoints-kpmg-adviser-offshore-debt-restructuring-2024-01-16/</guid></item><item><title>比亚迪首艘包船载着5000辆电动汽车起航前往欧洲-新华社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/byds-first-chartered-vessel-sets-sail-with-5000-evs-europe-xinhua-2024-01-16/</link><description>据官方媒体新华社周二报道，比亚迪首艘汽车包租船已从中国南方城市深圳起航，搭载 5,000 多辆电动汽车前往欧洲。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 10:52:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/byds-first-chartered-vessel-sets-sail-with-5000-evs-europe-xinhua-2024-01-16/</guid></item><item><title>印度选手纳加尔在墨尔本取得惊人胜利后保证获得巨额奖金</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/indias-nagal-guaranteed-big-payday-after-stunning-win-melbourne-2024-01-16/</link><description>印度排名第一的单打选手苏米特·纳加尔(Sumit Nagal)去年的银行账户里曾一度只剩下不到一千美元，因此在确保澳大利亚网球公开赛上的丰厚发薪日后，他周二的笑容也就不足为奇了。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 10:51:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/indias-nagal-guaranteed-big-payday-after-stunning-win-melbourne-2024-01-16/</guid></item><item><title>达沃斯 - 中国总理李克强：2023年中国经济增长预计为5.2%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/davos-chinese-premier-li-china-economy-growth-estimated-52-2023-2024-01-16/</link><description>中国国务院总理李强周二表示，中国经济已经回升上行，预计2023年增长5.2%左右，高于5%左右的官方目标。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 10:51:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/davos-chinese-premier-li-china-economy-growth-estimated-52-2023-2024-01-16/</guid></item><item><title>中国前国家主席之子出任副部长</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/former-chinese-presidents-son-becomes-vice-minister-2024-01-16/</link><description>中国前国家主席胡锦涛之子胡海峰周二被内阁任命为民政部副部长，从东部省份的一个小城市跃升为中央政府高层。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 10:37:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/former-chinese-presidents-son-becomes-vice-minister-2024-01-16/</guid></item><item><title>大韩航空、国泰航空的飞机在日本机场折断机翼；没有受伤</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/korean-air-plane-scrapes-cathay-pacific-airways-aircraft-japan-airport-2024-01-16/</link><description>大韩航空一名官员表示，周二，由于寒冷的天气，大韩航空和国泰航空的两架飞机在日本北部北海道岛的新千岁机场发生机翼折断。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 10:30:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/korean-air-plane-scrapes-cathay-pacific-airways-aircraft-japan-airport-2024-01-16/</guid></item><item><title>克里姆林宫拒绝讨论彭博社关于中国银行收紧对俄罗斯人的限制的报道</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/kremlin-declines-discuss-bloomberg-report-that-chinese-banks-tighten-curbs-2024-01-16/</link><description>克里姆林宫周二拒绝对彭博社的一篇报道发表评论，该报道称，由于担心美国的二次制裁，中国国有银行正在收紧对俄罗斯客户的融资限制，称这是一个高度敏感的话题。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 10:10:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/kremlin-declines-discuss-bloomberg-report-that-chinese-banks-tighten-curbs-2024-01-16/</guid></item><item><title>周二达沃斯有什么值得期待的</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/what-expect-davos-tuesday-2024-01-16/</link><description>世界经济论坛的主要议题周二拉开帷幕，中国总理李强的演讲成为首要议题。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 10:06:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/what-expect-davos-tuesday-2024-01-16/</guid></item><item><title>韩国和美国将在美国大选前提前开始国防费用谈判-媒体</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/south-korea-us-start-defence-cost-talks-early-before-us-elections-media-2024-01-16/</link><description>据当地媒体周二报道，韩国和美国已同意就如何分担驻韩美军的成本展开早期谈判，以便在唐纳德·特朗普可能连任总统之前达成协议。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 08:50:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/south-korea-us-start-defence-cost-talks-early-before-us-elections-media-2024-01-16/</guid></item><item><title>一些较富裕的中国人表示，随着经济放缓，他们买不起婚姻</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/some-wealthier-chinese-say-they-cant-afford-marriage-economy-slows-2024-01-16/</link><description>李泽楷决心尽快结婚，但像许多其他面临不确定经济前景的中国年轻人一样，这位富有的上海企业家不确定自己是否负担得起。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 08:44:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/some-wealthier-chinese-say-they-cant-afford-marriage-economy-slows-2024-01-16/</guid></item><item><title>台总理称内阁将按照以往惯例辞职</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-premier-says-cabinet-will-resign-accordance-with-past-practice-2024-01-16/</link><description>台湾行政院院长陈建仁周二表示，在执政党失去立法院多数席位后，内阁将在下个月新立法院召开前按照以往宪法惯例辞职。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 08:20:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-premier-says-cabinet-will-resign-accordance-with-past-practice-2024-01-16/</guid></item><item><title>日本东电将于二月下旬开始第四次释放福岛核电站水</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/japans-tepco-start-fourth-release-treated-fukushima-water-late-feb-2024-01-16/</link><description>周二，一名官员表示，东京电力公司 (Tepco) 计划于 2 月下旬开始第四次排放来自受损福岛第一核电站的处理过的放射性水，此举继续受到中国批评。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 08:03:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/japans-tepco-start-fourth-release-treated-fukushima-water-late-feb-2024-01-16/</guid></item><item><title>固态：电动汽车巨头追逐电池的“圣杯”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/solid-state-ev-giants-chase-holy-grail-batteries-2024-01-16/</link><description>固态电池有望为下一代电动汽车提供更多的能量存储、更长的行驶里程和更快的充电速度。然而，尽管经过数十年的研究和数十亿美元的投资，它们的未来仍然显得难以捉摸。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 06:08:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/solid-state-ev-giants-chase-holy-grail-batteries-2024-01-16/</guid></item></channel></rss>